{"tid":1564660,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"對女病患蹭腿又捏胸 色牙醫起訴","createTime":"2019-09-13T00:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T01:12:01.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b7337541b30f6ae0a6be22a04585f517ae3517c1","tid":1564660,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:48:31.000Z","msg":"一名傅姓牙醫去年4月替女病患看診，竟趁對方平躺無防備之際，用手磨蹭對方大腿，又大膽捏了胸部2次，因此吃上性騷擾官司，今天被新北地檢署起訴。<br />\n<br />\n女病患指控，傅姓牙醫不只在診所內對她毛手毛腳，2人第一次在診所外見面時，也曾趁她不注意，從她身後環抱她的胸口；女病患曾錄影質問牙醫為什麼突然抱她，牙醫回答抱歉，對於磨蹭大腿和捏胸部等情，他則以拍蚊子和不小心碰觸回應。<br />\n<br />\n偵訊時，傅姓牙醫承認曾地女病患看診，也認了談話內容，但對於性騷擾情事仍避重就輕，因此未被採信。<br />\n<br />\n檢方根據女病患的錄音、錄影內容，認定牙醫確實有性騷擾行為，最後依其先後2次行為，起訴2條性騷擾罪。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/5qpRmkn9VlGjS/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F5qpRmkn9VlGjS%2Fgiphy.gif&h=7d6d7a6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76a7887961540018e7de940463371e937b84f9e0","tid":1564660,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:49:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"95a8c9c7fd324de019dd3fbd34c6d108d1f9965e","tid":1564660,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:49:31.000Z","msg":"邊到？"},{"pid":"6f6786